'''Ariana''' (variants: Ariane, Arianna, Arianne, Arieana, Arionna, Arriana and Aryonna) is a feminine name. It is both an Italian simplification of the [[Greek language|Greek]] name [[Ariadne]] ("holy one"), and a [[Welsh language|Welsh]] name meaning "silver".[http://www.thinkbabynames.com/meaning/0/Ariana]
